snippet.title: This New Pokémon Roguelike is AMAZING - PokéRogue!
snippet.description:
PokeRogue brings the purest roguelike experience to Pokemon in a free-to-play browser game that you can play for yourself at pokerogue.net. It's jam-packed with so many different ways to play, making every run completely unique! Try it for yourself to support these awesome developers so we can see more easily accessible games like this one reach the audience it should!
